@node "slips" "Slipstream"

@{fg shine} Slipstream@{fg text}

           Is it possible to get Wipeout on your trusty Amiga? Lets find out! When
 I first heard of this game I didn't know what to think, could you really zoom round
 great rendered tracks in your spaceship at super speeds on your Amiga, well at last
 it seems you can. This game is only in it's very early stages so you can only
 therefore try out one track, the background graphics are great and the spaceship
