@node "mont" "MonteCarlo"

@{fg shine} MonteCarlo@{fg text}

           MonteCarlo tries to bring roulette to your own home, sadly I think it
 has failed. I really wanted to like this game as I have never played proper
 roulette in my life but I have to be truthful I hated this computer version.
 The main problem is the layout of the game on a separate WB window is awful, the
 background is green maybe to simulate the table cloth but this just anoys your
 eyes after a while. Another problem is there is no picture of a roulette wheel
 spinning so you just get a light flickering on whatever number the ball has last
 landed on, although not really a major problem it would of been nice to see
 something spinning and maybe a cheer sound effect. After all those problems
 if you really like roulette then this is probably for you.

