@node "agg" "Aggression"

@{fg shine} Aggression@{fg text}

           There have been a lot of shoot-em-up games over the years with the basic
 2D sprites, and thats about it, were all used to them so no one has ever complained.
 That was until this game, the graphics are just so good for a shoot-em-up, fly up and
 you can see under the spaceship, fly down and you can see the top of the spaceship.
 All the main sprites are rendered, the background isn't but that doesn't matter because
 it's the baddies and main spaceship that catch your attension. At moment the game
 is in it's early stages so you can only play one level. Even if you don't like shoot-
 em-ups this game might change your mind, i'm just waiting for the full game.

