@node "bbt" "BloodBath"

@{fg shine} Bloodbath@{fg text}

           If you liked Operation Wolf you'll love this, for you that don't know
 what Op Wolf is it's a shoot-em game, the idea is your looking out the persons
 eyes and you can see various baddies pop out from different places on the screen
 and you have to shoot them. The only difference with BloodBath is that the screen 
 doesn't scroll. The first thing that hits you is the graphics, they are just sooo
 good, the reason they are amazing is that the authors have filmed the people so
 it is real digitized levels and real digitzed people which adds to the fun of
 the game even more. The only real problem is the graphics are in black and white
 so don't be expecting colour, is suppose the graphics being in black and white is
 alright because the game at the moment is already 1.8meg and thats with black
 and white graphics. The intro itself takes up 1.8meg when decompacted even though
 it is very short, but it's worth it. There are only three levels to the game but
 if you have enough time to download 1.8meg you must get this just to see the
 graphics.

