@node "She" "Sheepshoot"

@{fg shine} SheepShoot@{fg text}

           Wayhay! What a game, this game is quite funny actually. The graphics are
 nicely done and cartoony but very simple. The idea of the game is to shoot the sheep
 that come shooting onto the screen, it's a bit like the clay pigeon shooting. The
 more sheep you shoot the more score you get and the higher the level gets. Thats it
 really but this game is nicely done and will keep you amused on a boring day.

