@node "ascii" "AsciiArt Pro V4"

@{fg shine} AsciiArt Pro V4@{fg text}

           If your into the world of colourful logos and wierd objects and you like
 doing them with text then this is the program for you. It is easy enough to use
 and even a begginer AsciiArtist could use this. It offers all the symbols in an
 easy point and click symbol bar, or if you prefer you can just use the keyboard.
 One of the programs most useful options is the IFF to Ascii. This will allow IFF
 pictures to be converted into Ascii without having to lift a finger, although the
 rendering of the picture takes a while the end results are pleasing and worth
 the wait. Ascii art can be done using a text editor but this program gives you
 some very useful options that only an Ascii Artist would need. This program is
 great and even got me doodling away.

 @{b}Avalible from@{ub} : Aminet or BBSes

 Overall 4 out of 5

     @{" Main Menu " link "Main" } @{" Utils Menu " link "Util" }
@endnode

@node "nsap" "NSA-Patch"

@{fg shine} NSA-Patch@{fg text}

           NSA-Patch is a very useful utility, the idea of it is to look through
 your program and replace any old speed commands with up to date new ones which
 will improve the speed of your program. I have used this program on nearly
 everything on my HD without any problems and alot of the programs have sped up
 nearly 2 or 3 times faster. Not everything will be sped up but on the programs
 it does speed up it's worth it. There isn't that much else to say about it but
 if you see it make sure you download it.

 @{b}Avalible from@{ub} : Aminet/BBSes

 Overall 4 out of 5

     @{" Main Menu " link "Main" } @{" Utils Menu " link "Util" }
@endnode

@node "tvap" "Tvap"

@{fg shine} TVAP V1.0@{fg text}

           TVAP V1.0 better known as 'The Very Anoying Program' is a WB Hack which
 every so often does something to your workbench like makes the memory disapear
 or moves a window about with out you touching it. This program is harmless but very
 useful, go round to a mates house and while there not there install it in there
 startup-sequence and watch with pleasure as they scan there HD with virus checkers
 and other such things. There isn't much point to this file but if you have a friend
 you'd like to anoy then download it.

