@node "vd" "ViewDIZ V1.4"

@{fg shine} ViewDIZ V1.4@{fg text}

           ViewDIZ simply allows you to look at a File_ID.DIZ without having to use
 a text editor/displayer, it also allows you to look at a File_ID.DIZ without
 unarchiving the file, at the moment it caters for lha, lzx, dms, txt, nfo, lzh and
 in future versions it will cater for everything. This program works really well
 with utils like DOpus and other disk managers. It has quite a lot of features for
 such a small program. If your constantly looking at file_ID_DIZ's then download this.

 @{b} Avalible from@{ub} : Aminet Util/Arc

 Overall 3 out of 5

